  "text": "However, \u03c6 has sublinear growth on \u2126 As a consequence of the growth lemma we have an obstruction for nonplanar one ended ESWMT-surfaces with finite total curvature in R 3 . This is an evidence about the premise that the theory of ESWMT-surfaces is quite similar to the theory of minimal surfaces, even more if we note that there is not such obstruction for harmonic surfaces of finite total curvature, see [CITATION_1] .",
